These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-1::.
Hobby: cooking, writing, traveling, reading
Beverage: tea, 7up, lemonade, soy-milk
Flower: dahlia, tulip, poppy, begonia
Sport: rowing, baseball, snowboarding, golf
 1. Beverage:tea is on the right of Beverage:7up##1
 2. Hobby:cooking is in an even position##4
 3. Flower:dahlia is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1
 4. Flower:poppy is on the right of Hobby:reading##1
 5. Beverage:tea is on the left or right of Beverage:7up##3
 6. Sport:rowing is on the left of Hobby:writing##1
 7. Flower:tulip == Hobby:traveling##1
 8. Sport:snowboarding is in an even position##4
 9. Sport:rowing is between Sport:golf and Beverage:soy-milk##2
10. Hobby:cooking == Sport:golf##1
11. Beverage:lemonade == Hobby:reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Hobby          | traveling  | cooking    | reading    | writing   |
| Beverage   | 7up     | tea   | lemonade       | soy-milk    |
| Flower   | tulip | dahlia | begonia    | poppy |
| Sport           | baseball | golf       | rowing | snowboarding     |

