.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-4-2::.
Flower: zinnia, daisy, azalea, lily
Music-Genre: trance, punk, pop, jazz
House: cottage, wooden, modern, colonial
Movie-Genre: documentary, western, disaster, romance
 1. Music-Genre:jazz is in an even position##4
 2. House:wooden is on the left of Movie-Genre:western##1
 3. Music-Genre:punk is on the right of Flower:azalea##1
 4. Flower:daisy == House:cottage##1
 5. Movie-Genre:romance is on the right of Flower:zinnia##1
 6. House:cottage is on the left or right of House:modern##3
 7. Flower:lily is on the right of Flower:azalea##1
 8. House:colonial is on the left or right of Movie-Genre:documentary##3
 9. House:modern is on the far left or far right##3
10. Flower:azalea is in an odd position##4
11. House:modern == Music-Genre:pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |    3     |     4      |
| Flower          | zinnia  | daisy    | azalea     | lily       |
| Music-Genre         | pop | jazz | trance   | punk |
| House   | modern | cottage   | wooden   | colonial    |
| Movie-Genre         | disaster | romance  | documentary | western   |

